title: Republic Act No. 11313 - Safe Spaces Act (Bawal Bastos Law)
originalName: Republic Act No. 11313 - Safe Spaces Act.pdf
description: An act defining gender-based sexual harassment in streets, public spaces, online, workplaces, and educational or training institutions, providing protective measures and prescribing penalties therefor.

title: Republic Act No. 10173 - Data Privacy Act of 2012
originalName: Republic Act No. 10173 - Data Privacy Act.pdf
description: An act protecting individual personal information in information and communications systems in the government and the private sector, creating for this purpose the National Privacy Commission.

title: Republic Act No. 11232 - Revised Corporation Code of the Philippines
originalName: Republic Act No. 11232 - Revised Corporation Code.pdf
description: An act providing for the revised corporation code of the Philippines, modernizing corporate governance, enhancing investor protection, and promoting ease of doing business.

title: Supreme Court Decision - People vs. Sandiganbayan (G.R. No. 234567)
description: Supreme Court decision on criminal jurisdiction and procedural matters involving the Sandiganbayan.

title: Executive Order No. 123 - Creation of Task Force
description: Creating a task force to address specific government initiatives and reforms.

title: 1987 Constitution of the Republic of the Philippines
description: The fundamental law of the Philippines, ratified in 1987 following the People Power Revolution.
